sellerCard.description:
I am Israr Ahmed, A professional framer & webflow designer. I've built 50+ sites on these platforms and earned some great reviews over the last couple of months. I Measure my Success by Your Satisfaction.

"I am not Afraid of Trying Again. I am Afraid of Making my Clients Feel Wasted" ,ISRAR AHMED

description.content:
Hey, Are you looking for someone to get your website ready on Framer? Then, you're in the right place.


INTRODUCTION:

Hi, I am Israr Ahmed, A professional framer developer. I've built over 50+ framer sites over the last couple of months and Completed over 10 Figma to framer projects with my clients and have earned their satisfaction. I am not the best one But, I'm confident that I can make you believe it Through my work.


What I Provide:


Figma To Framer: We can work together If you have the Design for your website ready in a Figma file and now you want to convert it into a responsive framer site with some beautiful complex animations.


Framer Fixes: I can help you If you have anything in your Framer Project that is not looking/working Perfectly. This includes Fixes for CMS, Components, Code Components, Effects & Animations, and more.


Framer site Design & Redesign: I can design and develop your website in Framer from scratch or even redesign your old site. For this having a reference is required, as I need to know what you're looking for by the end of it.


Click the "Contact Me" button Now and let's have a Chat.



I DON'T WORK FOR ANY P0*N OR ADULT WEB.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I share my Figma project with you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Click the "Share" button at the top right corner of your Figma project, add my email there, give the role of "Editor," and click Invite, and I'll be able to join the project.

You can get me Figma email by placing an order or asking me in chat...

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I have look at some of your previous projects?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! you can have a look at some of my previous projects from my portfolio section.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you know "Framer Motion"?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sorry, Framer Motion is not something that I work with. But, I can help you with Framer code components using my ReactJS skills.

reviews.comment:
I had the rare pleasure of working with Israr on converting my website from Figma to Webflow. What stood out wasn't just his technical skill, but his attention to the small things that make a design feel right.

Most developers treat feedback as a burden. Israr treated it as a tool to get things perfect. He responded quickly, made revisions promptly, and stayed patient through multiple rounds of refinement.

Perhaps most valuable was his clear communication. Good communication in software projects is surprisingly rare, and it makes an enormous difference. Israr has it.

If you're looking for someone who will care about your project as much as you do, hire Israr. I certainly will again.

I had an excellent experience working with Israr to bring my Figma design to life on Framer. He was professional, efficient, and paid great attention to detail. The final result perfectly matched my original vision, with seamless animations and a clean, responsive layout. Communication was clear throughout the process, and he ensured that every aspect of the site was functional and user-friendly.

I highly recommend Israr for anyone looking for a skilled developer to translate designs into fully functional websites. Im thrilled with the outcome and look forward to collaborating again in the future!

seller_response.comment: I feel like I can't thank you enough for this masterpiece... Thanks,

reviews.comment: I loved working with Israr, he was efficient, quick and kind. I will work with him again. He also created multiple declination of my webpage to accommodate various sizes of tablets and mobile screen to ensure maximum responsiveness. Great job !

seller_response.comment: Thanks for the kind words sir,

reviews.comment: Ive loved working with Israr I believe he is right for me. He did an outstanding job for two gig consecutively. Will work with him again. Thank you so much.

seller_response.comment: Most welcome sir, I am also looking forward to future collaboration...

reviews.comment: Very talented and amazing guy. Got it done very quick and efficient. Thanks for helping me out and I look forward to our future collaboration
